name: Glass UI - Landing page (glassmorphism)
description:
Figma Glassmorphism Landing Page


Get started with this free example of landing page inspired by glassmorphism based on the Glass UI design system. The design includes both dark and light versions.


Learn more about Glass UI


Glass UI is a modern UI library based on the glassmorphism design specifications which includes hundreds of web components, sections, and example pages.


  • Learn more about Glass UI: ui.glass
  • Learn more about Themesberg: themesberg.com
